540
01:19:05,120 --> 01:19:06,810
Midnight?

541
01:19:30,340 --> 01:19:32,310
Know this one?

542
01:19:37,410 --> 01:19:39,880
"Here's how many nights
and a day

543
01:19:39,920 --> 01:19:41,890
"Here's how long
you've been away

544
01:19:41,920 --> 01:19:44,390
"It was to be
our last time apart

545
01:19:44,420 --> 01:19:47,050
"The last strain
on my shipwrecked heart

546
01:19:47,090 --> 01:19:49,820
"You said you'd be back
in spring

547
01:19:49,860 --> 01:19:52,560
"A time for sweetness
and whispering

548
01:19:52,600 --> 01:19:55,360
