to go your way

552
01:20:08,310 --> 01:20:10,470
"I'll remember our love
as a happy day

553
01:20:10,510 --> 01:20:13,010
"I'll hit the road,
a smile on my face

554
01:20:13,050 --> 01:20:15,450
"I'll go bask in the sun
some other place

555
01:20:15,490 --> 01:20:18,010
"Sorrows won't make me
give up my life

556
01:20:18,060 --> 01:20:21,420
"I'm not as patient
as a sailor's wife"

557
01:20:41,650 --> 01:20:45,450
