It was a drag.

563
01:21:04,470 --> 01:21:07,670
It wasn't the first time.

564
01:21:07,700 --> 01:21:10,200
Then...

565
01:21:10,240 --> 01:21:12,440
he got into bed...

566
01:21:12,480 --> 01:21:18,070
and made love to me trying to be
gentle so as not to wake me.

567
01:21:18,120 --> 01:21:20,020
