568
01:21:20,050 --> 01:21:22,250
Sometimes he says to me...

569
01:21:22,290 --> 01:21:25,410
"Let go. Play dead."

570
01:21:25,460 --> 01:21:27,510
When I met him...

571
01:21:27,560 --> 01:21:32,430
at first, right after
my father's death...

572
01:21:32,460 --> 01:21:35,330
