573
01:21:35,370 --> 01:21:38,860
Now he criticizes me for things.

574
01:21:38,900 --> 01:21:41,270
Things I don't understand.

575
01:21:42,570 --> 01:21:45,200
For him, it all matters:

576
01:21:45,240 --> 01:21:49,370
my past, my future,
my present, and my death...

577
01:21:53,080 --> 01:21:57,210
I often wonder what my father
would've thought of him...

578
01:21:58,820 --> 01:22:01,050
and of me today.

579
01:22:02,990 --> 01:22:06,620
I am...l'm what I am.

580
01:22:49,010 --> 01:22:50,870
It's very late.

581
01:22:58,980 --> 01:23:01,250
