582
01:23:02,490 --> 01:23:05,920
Everyone's going.
We're the last.

583
01:23:06,960 --> 01:23:08,860
I'm leaving.

584
01:23:19,270 --> 01:23:22,900
It's like a dream for me,
being with you.

585
01:23:22,940 --> 01:23:25,240
Like an unusually deep dream.

586
01:23:25,280 --> 01:23:28,710
Only deep sleep
makes you dream like that.

587
01:23:34,920 --> 01:23:38,790
Sitting beside you this way...

588
01:23:38,820 --> 01:23:41,020
is like eternity.

589
01:23:43,790 --> 01:23:45,960
The moment I saw you...

590
01:23:46,000 --> 01:23:48,560
I knew I was destined
to love you.

591
01:23:48,600 --> 01:23:50,900
I'll say it once and for all:

592
01:23:50,930 --> 01:23:53,900
I love you, Mireille,
more than anything.

593
01:23:53,940 --> 01:23:55,730
We must fall in love!

594
01:23:55,770 --> 01:24:00,900
Unaware of it, wordlessly...
It's too late!

595
01:24:00,940 --> 01:24:02,640
Pretend you didn't hear that...

596
01:24:02,680 --> 01:24:05,080
Time to shut up. I will.

597
01:24:05,120 --> 01:24:07,640
After 20 years of battling,
silence.

598
01:24:07,680 --> 01:24:11,810
To think that your body
will age...

599
01:24:11,860 --> 01:24:14,480
Shriveled breasts
and more wrinkles, Mireille...

600
01:24:14,520 --> 01:24:17,320
On your belly, under your ass.

601
01:24:17,360 --> 01:24:18,590
