602
01:24:18,630 --> 01:24:20,720
You see, Mireille, love...

603
01:24:20,760 --> 01:24:22,430
Iove without regrets...

604
01:24:22,470 --> 01:24:24,760
Iove without
nasty afterthoughts...

605
01:24:24,800 --> 01:24:27,460
Say come, I'll come,
say smile, I'll smile...

606
01:24:27,500 --> 01:24:30,200
We'll sleep together
for as long as you want...

607
01:24:30,240 --> 01:24:34,300
I want to work with you,
form an unbeatable team...

608
01:24:34,340 --> 01:24:37,470
Whatever our signs,
Libra or Leo, I'll sign up!

609
01:24:37,510 --> 01:24:42,110
Maybe Florence, seeing
our strength, will join us...

610
01:24:42,150 --> 01:24:45,750
You and Florence and me...
I'll be the go-between lover...

611
01:24:45,790 --> 01:24:47,780
It should be so moving.

612
01:24:47,820 --> 01:24:49,550
Back and forth I go!

613
01:24:49,590 --> 01:24:52,930
Alone, you couldn't jolt me out
of my shell...

614
01:24:52,960 --> 01:24:54,930
Together,
we'll change our habits...

615
01:24:54,970 --> 01:24:58,300
We'll leave Paris,
maybe even France.

616
01:24:58,340 --> 01:25:00,240
And out of love for me, Alex...

617
01:25:00,270 --> 01:25:02,430
you'll stop
destroying yourself...

618
01:25:02,470 --> 01:25:04,030
You'll respect the warmth
of your blood...

619
01:25:04,070 --> 01:25:05,470
your serene presence...

620
01:25:05,510 --> 01:25:09,210
your clear perception,
your gentle feelings...

621
01:25:09,250 --> 01:25:12,650
Under your impulse,
our melancholy will fade away.

622
01:25:12,680 --> 01:25:14,980
